{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "10", "m": "04", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "08", "M": "57", "S": "41"}}, "news": [{"title": "New Noida land rates at par with YEIDA at \u20b94,300 per sq meters", "para": "Noida Authority has set land acquisition rates for the upcoming phases of New Noida. The Dadri-Noida-Ghaziabad Investment Region project will span 209 sq km. Land rates for the third and fourth phases are fixed at Rs 4,300 per sqm. This move aims to expedite the development of a modern industrial hub.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/new-noidas-land-rates-align-with-yeida-at-4300-per-sqm-amid-major-development-project/130157563?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-115634/130157563.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Bombay HC directs MMRDA to refund \u20b9646 crore to Reliance Industries", "para": "Bombay High Court has ordered the MMRDA to refund Rs 646 crore to Reliance Industries Limited, setting aside penalties for an alleged delay in completing a convention centre. The court deemed the penalty levy arbitrary and unreasonable, stating MMRDA was obligated to apply a six-year extension clause to the project.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/bombay-hc-orders-mmrda-to-refund-646-crore-to-reliance-industries-landmark-judgment/130157490?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-105826/130157490.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "OC probe widens as checks reveal lapses, 14 of 22 buildings incomplete in Gurugram", "para": "An ongoing probe into occupation certificate irregularities in Gurugram has uncovered widespread violations. A joint team inspected 22 buildings in Sector 70A, finding at least 14 incomplete structures were granted OCs. Architects in